body:
Dating Harry Styles would include…

A/N: this has probably been done before but here’s my rendition 🤷🏻‍♀️ also I wanted to attack @foreverhlessed and @smokeinherperfume

Start of relationship:

• him creeping your Instagram a little bit to see if you’re in a relationship or not prior to making a move

• getting a notification from him accidentally liking a picture from 2 years ago

• “did you just like my picture?”

“… so it’s some nice weather we’re having, yeah?”

• having plans for this extravagant first date, but settling on a simple night in where you two spend hours talking and eating whatever is leftover of the takeout he brought

• giving subtle hints of how you’d love a second date, and him not picking up on said hints so he just blantanly asks you again although the thought of you saying no is eating him alive

• the grin of relief that washes over his face when you agree to the date; his dimples on full display

• him trying his best to keep you his dirty little secret as your relationship with him is becoming a bit more serious *alexa, play The All-American Rejects*

• but for real, him being concerned about how people will react to his relationship with you and you really not knowing what to expect… but him not letting that affect how he feels about you in the slightest

• his family being the first to know once you both make official

• “So Mum, there’s this girl”

“I’ve heard”

“Huh?”

“Gemma told me”

• *shows off a picture of you to a friend*

“And she’s even prettier in person, you wouldn’t believe”

• being welcomed with open arms by his family, and vise versa for him with yours… although there’s some bugging and teasing by certain family members, naturally

• showing up with flowers unexpectedly

• the wave of how much you love this man hitting you like a brick freaking wall

Later in the relationship:

• all the kisses (forehead, cheek, full on makeout, etc)

• being past the point of explaining how badly you each crave the others presence, people just know

• shamelessly walking around in whatever you want while at home together (clothing optional)

• *intro of Mr. Brightside starts playing during a long road trip*

*both slowly glances at each other knowingly*

6 seconds later, in unison: COMING OUT OF MY CAGE AND I’VE BEEN DOING JUST FINE

• sitting on his lap, his arms wrapped tightly around your middle, as he leans against your back; smiling aimlessly while showing you bits of the new album he’s working on

• giving shoulder rubs during those late nights he’s awake writing down lyrics

• daily gif conversations

• “babe, I’m at Starbucks. Want anything?”

• being his Dunkirk and all other premieres plus one

• him being excited to take you traveling, showing you all of his favourite little spots at each destination

• having a designated spot at his concerts so he knows just where to look for when he’s dedicating the next song to you

• admiring how good he looks in each and every one of those damn tour suits

• *walks into the kitchen to the smell of him cooking something*

“Ooh can I try?”

“JOEY DOESNT SHARE FOOD” - *storms away*

• begging him to spend New Years in NYC, and him obliging with the agreement that the two of you are kissing once the clock strikes 12

• attempting to go ice skating in the winter and trying your best to not recreate his scene in the Night Changes video

• him crawling into bed after a fight, pulling you right up to his chest saying he refuses to go to sleep upset; trailing the softest kisses along your shoulder and collarbone as he does so

• the best sex. period.

• rom-com movie marathons

• watching the packers play during football season just so he’ll shut up about it

• him injuring himself while performing a simple task, and you having to take care of him

• “are you alright?”

“Physically, I’m fine”

“No”

“Emotionally…”

“Don’t”

“IM BRUISED”

• pouting when what makes you beautiful comes on and he instantly turns it down to get a ride out of you; only to turn it back up seconds later and screaming the lyrics with you

• emotional reunions in the middle of airports after long times apart

• “I’m home now bub, m’all yours”

• mindlessly running your hand through his curls as he tiredly rests on your lap

• him opening your door for you in the pouring rain, but making sure he stops your for a deep kiss before letting you run past; channelling your inner Noah and Allie.

• hearing him sing along to the likes of She Will Be Loved and other sappy songs from the shower, only to go in an join him shortly after

• fangirling hard together over attending the concerts of some of your favourite artists

• the constant tellings and gestures of the love you two share, privately and publicly

• an eventual vow to be each other’s “person” forever

• begging him to spend New Years in NYC, and him obliging with the agreement that the two of you are kissing once the clock strikes 12

• attempting to go ice skating in the winter and trying your best to not recreate his scene in the Night Changes video

• him crawling into bed after a fight, pulling you right up to his chest saying he refuses to go to sleep upset; trailing the softest kisses along your shoulder and collarbone as he does so

• the best sex. period.

• rom-com movie marathons

• watching the packers play during football season just so he’ll shut up about it

• him injuring himself while performing a simple task, and you having to take care of him

• “are you alright?”

“Physically, I’m fine”

“No”

“Emotionally…”

“Don’t”

“IM BRUISED”

• pouting when what makes you beautiful comes on and he instantly turns it down to get a ride out of you; only to turn it back up seconds later and screaming the lyrics with you

• emotional reunions in the middle of airports after long times apart

• “I’m home now bub, m’all yours”

• mindlessly running your hand through his curls as he tiredly rests on your lap

• him opening your door for you in the pouring rain, but making sure he stops your for a deep kiss before letting you run past; channelling your inner Noah and Allie.

• hearing him sing along to the likes of She Will Be Loved and other sappy songs from the shower, only to go in an join him shortly after

• fangirling hard together over attending the concerts of some of your favourite artists

• the constant tellings and gestures of the love you two share, privately and publicly

• an eventual vow to be each other’s “person” forever
